{"tid":1708290,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"梁天琦: 「時代革命」的意思, 並非武攻, 而是改變民心, 反思香港政制前途","createTime":"2019-11-11T14:05:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T15:35:34.000Z","uid":134071,"like":70,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"e3ca7298808f62775bb21292c6dd4ce6f4a38070","tid":1708290,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T14:05:46.000Z","msg":"好掛住梁天琦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mingpaocanada.com/van/htm/News/20161207/HK-gma1h_r.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mingpaocanada.com%2Fvan%2Fhtm%2FNews%2F20161207%2FHK-gma1h_r.htm&d=KwnMNtvToZrWMgCiTfGJQX4WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=fe6aef30\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.mingpaocanada.com/van/htm/News/20161207/HK-gma1h_r.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n曾高呼要「時代革命」的梁天琦（圖）說，<strong>時代革命的意思是要改變民心，反思香港政制前途。他指「時代革命」並非一般人認為「揸支槍去進攻邊度」</strong>，「我不知大家成日問時代革命去了哪裏，是不是想問幾時有人進攻禮賓府，如果有人是這樣想，抱歉，似乎大家理解有錯」。（鄧宗弘攝）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/g51mchp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg51mchp.jpg&h=4d375703&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"744db2857cf48b5cf4ecea342cc27bc443c60d4c","tid":1708290,"uid":134071,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T14:05:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"http://thestandnews.com/society/%E8%A2%AB%E6%8B%92%E5%8F%83%E9%81%B8-%E6%A2%81%E5%A4%A9%E7%90%A6-%E6%9C%89%E5%A6%82%E7%B5%82%E8%BA%AB%E5%89%9D%E5%A5%AA%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E6%AC%8A%E5%88%A9-%E9%AB%94%E5%88%B6%E5%A4%96%E7%9F%9B%E7%9B%BE%E5%92%8C%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81%E6%9C%83%E6%9B%B4%E6%BF%80-%E6%96%99%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%9F%E6%B4%BE%E6%AF%8F%E5%8D%80%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%80%E5%B8%AD/?fb_comment_id=1065755643516196_1065767816848312\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258B%2592%25E5%258F%2583%25E9%2581%25B8-%25E6%25A2%2581%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E7%2590%25A6-%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%25A6%2582%25E7%25B5%2582%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E5%2589%259D%25E5%25A5%25AA%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%25B2%25BB%25E6%25AC%258A%25E5%2588%25A9-%25E9%25AB%2594%25E5%2588%25B6%25E5%25A4%2596%25E7%259F%259B%25E7%259B%25BE%25E5%2592%258C%25E8%25A1%259D%25E7%25AA%2581%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%259B%25B4%25E6%25BF%2580-%25E6%2596%2599%25E6%259C%25AC%25E5%259C%259F%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E6%25AF%258F%25E5%258D%2580%25E6%259C%2589%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25B8%25AD%2F%3Ffb_comment_id%3D1065755643516196_1065767816848312&d=KwnMNtvToZrWMgCiTfGJQX4WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=44fb75d9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258B%2592%25E5%258F%2583%25E9%2581%25B8-%25E6%25A2%2581%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E7%2590%25A6-%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%25A6%2582%25E7%25B5%2582%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E5%2589%259D%25E5%25A5%25AA%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%25B2%25BB%25E6%25AC%258A%25E5%2588%25A9-%25E9%25AB%2594%25E5%2588%25B6%25E5%25A4%2596%25E7%259F%259B%25E7%259B%25BE%25E5%2592%258C%25E8%25A1%259D%25E7%25AA%2581%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%259B%25B4%25E6%25BF%2580-%25E6%2596%2599%25E6%259C%25AC%25E5%259C%259F%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E6%25AF%258F%25E5%258D%2580%25E6%259C%2589%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25B8%25AD%2F%3Ffb_comment_id%3D1065755643516196_1065767816848312&h=4872f1e4\" target=\"_blank\">http://thestandnews.com/society/%E8%A2%AB%E6%8B%92%E5%8F%83%E9%81%B8-%E6%A2%81%E5%A4%A9%E7%90%A6-%E6%9C%89%E5%A6%82%E7%B5%82%E8%BA%AB%E5%89%9D%E5%A5%AA%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E6%AC%8A%E5%88%A9-%E9%AB%94%E5%88%B6%E5%A4%96%E7%9F%9B%E7%9B%BE%E5%92%8C%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81%E6%9C%83%E6%9B%B4%E6%BF%80-%E6%96%99%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%9F%E6%B4%BE%E6%AF%8F%E5%8D%80%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%80%E5%B8%AD/?fb_comment_id=1065755643516196_1065767816848312</a></span><br />\n<br />\n梁天琦又解釋，革命不只街頭運動，包括傳播和組織的工作，取得民心，也是革命一部份，令到我們這一代人和下一代人也是和我們一樣，去想香港變成怎樣的地方，他形容，<strong>改變民心才是最重要。</strong>"},{"pid":"3ff9849d8bbe4f356b67df048bbaf40a2be60e41","tid":1708290,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T14:06:51.000Z","msg":"不如以後手足有咩不完美行為 玩膠改篇高官/狗方新聞稿去對外解釋算啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1708276\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1708276</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5f64ed5bfca1679f130a39d5ceb9eb9cbdb5f444","tid":1708290,"uid":329466,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T14:07:14.000Z","msg":"又囉天琦黎講"},{"pid":"4f1d1435eaccdfaddb0438cba36c3bd2b3d4f502","tid":1708290,"uid":134071,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T14:07:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%96%87%E6%91%98/article/20160814/s00022/1471137079445\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%2596%2587%25E6%2591%2598%2Farticle%2F20160814%2Fs00022%2F1471137079445&d=KwnMNtvToZrWMgCiTfGJQX4WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=063377ab\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%2596%2587%25E6%2591%2598%2Farticle%2F20160814%2Fs00022%2F1471137079445&h=c47195b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%96%87%E6%91%98/article/20160814/s00022/1471137079445</a><br />\n<br />\n什麼人訪問什麼人﹕<strong>梁天琦︰革命當然是長線的</strong>（文：Tam Daniel） (09:10)<br />\n<br />\n....<br />\n譚︰呈請若失敗了，下一步是怎樣？<br />\n<br />\n梁︰這樣的話，就代表社會上全部方法用盡，都無法得到應有公義。好理性的結論就是，只有革命一條路，這是事實。問題只是怎樣去實現。<strong>我覺得我們做的工夫，都是沿着這條路去走︰影響社會，影響民心。</strong>這半年我覺得我們有一定的成績。<br />\n<br />\n譚︰這是兩種時間觀呢，革命和組織工作。<br />\n<br />\n梁︰革命當然是長線的，難道是一天半天嗎。辛亥革命固然指辛亥年發生的武昌起義，但我們更泛指多場起義，<strong>16年的時間</strong>。我和你講下星期會成功，或有一個確切的時間，一聽就知道是騙人啦。"},{"pid":"865c746f2b6bd0fef253eeb79430e528ce9b6bb8","tid":1708290,"uid":134071,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"5f64ed5bfca1679f130a39d5ceb9eb9cbdb5f444","tid":1708290,"uid":329466,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T14:07:14.000Z","msg":"又囉天琦黎講"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T14:10:26.000Z","msg":"無問題<br />\n<br />\n「時代革命」係由梁天琦發起, 佢有權